                                <p class="mb-2" style="font-size: 14px; color: #656565;">Narrow down your candidates</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-2 m-0 text-right">
                                <a class="card-link rotateLink2" data-toggle="collapse" style="color:black;"
